                    <span>Every Business is a Growth Business is full of insights that can be applied in every business.  The book confirms my philosophy on how to grow businessess profitably.  It has a set of valuable applications.  Chapter Three, Commonsense and Capital, is a must read for those who want to  sharpen their business acumen.</span>
                  
